message.content:
1. CBD improved emotional facial affect recognition at 60% emotional intensity.
2. This improvement was in comparison to a placebo.
3. THC was detrimental to the recognition of ambiguous faces.
4. The detrimental effect of THC was observed at 40% intensity.
